Class FocusModel

java.lang.Object
org.eclipse.gef.common.adapt.IAdaptable.Bound.Impl<IViewer>
org.eclipse.gef.mvc.fx.models.FocusModel
All Implemented Interfaces:
IAdaptable.Bound<IViewer>, IDisposable
public class FocusModel extends IAdaptable.Bound.Impl<IViewer> implements IDisposable
The FocusModel stores the IContentPart which has keyboard focus. Note that you are responsible for synchronizing keyboard focus with the model.
